title: FC Ritm Alekseyevka
text: FC Ritm Alekseyevka () was a Russian <a href="association%20football">football</a> team from <a href="Alexeyevka%2C%20Belgorod%20Oblast">Alexeyevka</a>. It played professionally in 1991, 1992 and 1995. Their best result was 8th place in Zone 2 of the <a href="Russian%20Second%20Division">Russian Second Division</a> in 1992.
